1️⃣ How to install

1. Create a directory where you want ScidUp to live; "installation" means just
   moving this directory.
2. Extract the archive into that directory.

If you cannot extract .tar.gz
- Install 7-Zip, then right-click the file and select "Extract Here".

For instance:
1. Right-click the downloaded .tar.gz and extract it.
2. Rename the extracted folder to "ScidUp" (optional).
3. Move the folder somewhere convenient (e.g. your Desktop or Documents).

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2️⃣ How to run

1. Open the bin folder.
2. Double-click scid-up.exe.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

3️⃣ Where are my settings?

ScidUp stores settings under:
- %APPDATA%\\scid-up

You can also set SCIDUP_CONFIG_HOME to use a custom settings directory.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

4️⃣ Something broken? Report it, please!

- Create a new issue: https://github.com/bahmanm/scid-up/issues/new
- See existing issues: https://github.com/bahmanm/scid-up/issues

When reporting a bug, please include:
- Windows version
- The ScidUp release
- A screenshot of the error (or any console output)

